 19  /-- A complete distributive lattice is a bit stronger than the name might
 20    suggest; perhaps completely distributive lattice is more descriptive,
 21    as this class includes a requirement that the lattice join
 22    distribute over *arbitrary* infima, and similarly for the dual. -/
